    <item>
      <title>乱城</title>
      <link>https://www.zhurongshuo.com/posts/2020/08/0206/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Aug 2020 22:30:04 +0800</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://www.zhurongshuo.com/posts/2020/08/0206/</guid>
      <description>&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;城池破碎，深夜买醉。兵戎不退，你无畏。身边，有他相背。我不配。城南残垣，栀子山前。明珠断线，亲归我无回。叛城，无谓。只为你媚。引军东去，信你北，速退。你痴他倔，城碎，城碎，血染水中弯月。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;你是英雄遗孀，我是投敌叛将。庆功宴上，明眸皓齿，浅笑嫣嫣，正是往昔模样。一曲断红殇，怕是只断我肠。敌王笑，叛城为红孀。夜。白刃入肋，你流泪。轻抚青丝，好累。依稀光华，你啐我醉，且睡。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;</description>
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>重楼</title>
      <link>https://www.zhurongshuo.com/posts/2020/08/0205/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Aug 2020 22:25:04 +0800</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://www.zhurongshuo.com/posts/2020/08/0205/</guid>
      <description>&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;花开树下你正忧，离别秋，两相愁。衣绯白雪，不胜娇羞。三十轮回苦，是分时，悔未说。恍然十年月下烛，忘忧。清泪画月沟，伊人笑，心纠。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;</description>
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>西帘</title>
      <link>https://www.zhurongshuo.com/posts/2020/08/0204/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Aug 2020 22:22:04 +0800</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://www.zhurongshuo.com/posts/2020/08/0204/</guid>
      <description>&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;卷西帘，晴当空，边柱青鸟路。星捞起，饮酒狂盅，千种粟，曾既马前布。梦中比邻，寒江双手，千年圆烟，禅蝉鸣泣，低吟浅笑一场松。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;</description>
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>弃胡</title>
      <link>https://www.zhurongshuo.com/posts/2020/08/0203/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Aug 2020 22:20:04 +0800</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://www.zhurongshuo.com/posts/2020/08/0203/</guid>
      <description>&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;胡人夜舞，山栾阻舟雾。君陌等，千年路。萍细雨，不相负，谁道婆娑苦。红泥重，烟波，凝固。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;</description>
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>临江仙</title>
      <link>https://www.zhurongshuo.com/posts/2020/08/0202/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Aug 2020 22:19:04 +0800</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://www.zhurongshuo.com/posts/2020/08/0202/</guid>
      <description>&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;大笑伤门秦夜舞，三番遮幕，可怒?红袖暖楼阁，亲不顾，只教狂徒侮，罢了，且负。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;</description>
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>谢秋娘</title>
      <link>https://www.zhurongshuo.com/posts/2020/08/0201/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Aug 2020 22:18:04 +0800</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://www.zhurongshuo.com/posts/2020/08/0201/</guid>
      <description>&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;青阁暖，玉殒风催烛。街亭小喧人怒，稚手推缘赴。浅笑，舒眉，心慕，何故？&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;</description>
    </item>
    
